    "Hess' thesis, a study of biographies of <a href=\"/passerig\">Giovanni Battista Passeri</a>, was accepted in 1926 and published in 1928.": [],
    "He remained in Munich, working on a scholarly facsimile edition of Passeri's <em>Vite</em>, <em>Die k\u00fcnstlerbiographien von Giovanni Battista Passeri</em>, financed through a grant, which he published in 1934.": [
